Packet Structures changed

1. Packet format for client joined changed.
    has now the color and the address(ip) from it joined.

    Packet format NOW: JUST_JOINED#username/Time/status/color
    Packet format Earlier: JUST_JOINED#username/Time/address/status/color


Changes in the addUser Method

    addUser NOW : private void adduser(String username)
    addUser Earlier : private void adduser(String username,String address,String status,int color)
    Explanation: The client who just joined in will be added with the tooltip showing its ip-status(blank if not set) and corresponding color.